#### CommitReferenceFilter

- Commit: <%= commit.to_reference %>
- Commit in another project: <%= xcommit.to_reference(project) %>
- Ignored in code: `<%= commit.to_reference %>`
- Ignored in links: [Link to <%= commit.to_reference %>](#commit-link)
