### Inline Diffs

With inline diffs tags you can display {+ additions +} or [- deletions -].

The wrapping tags can be either curly braces or square brackets [+ additions +] or {- deletions -}.

Examples:

```
- {+ additions +}
- [+ additions +]
- {- deletions -}
- [- deletions -]
```

However the wrapping tags cannot be mixed as such:

```
- {+ additions +]
- [+ additions +}
- {- deletions -]
- [- deletions -}
```

